<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>메인 페이지</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { background-color: #f8f9fa; font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif; }
        .hero-section { background: white; padding: 60px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6; }
        .board-card { transition: transform 0.2s; border: none; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .board-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); }
        .nav-link { font-weight: 500; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-white sticky-top shadow-sm">
    <div class="container">
        <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold text-primary" href="/">MY SERVICE</a>
        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
            <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                {{#user}}
                    <li class="nav-item d-flex align-items-center">
                        <span class="nav-link px-3 text-dark"><strong>{{nickname}}</strong>님 환영합니다!</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item d-flex align-items-center">
                        <a class="nav-link px-3" href="/logout">로그아웃</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item d-flex align-items-center">
                        <a class="nav-link btn btn-outline-success ms-lg-2" href="/update/{{username}}">회원 수정</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item d-flex align-items-center">
                        <form action="/delete/{{username}}" method="post" onsubmit="return confirm('정말 탈퇴하시겠습니까?');" style="margin: 0;">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-danger ms-lg-2">회원 탈퇴</button>
                        </form>
                    </li>
                {{/user}}

                {{^user}}
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link px-3" href="/login">로그인</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link btn btn-outline-primary ms-lg-2" href="/join">회원가입</a></li>
                {{/user}}
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

<header class="hero-section text-center">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold">환영합니다!</h1>
        <p class="lead text-muted">원하는 게시판을 선택하여 다양한 이야기를 나누어보세요.</p>
    </div>
</header>

<main class="container my-5">
    <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card h-100 board-card">
                <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
                    <h3 class="card-title h5 fw-bold">추천 게시판</h3>
                    <p class="card-text text-muted small">게임 추천</p>
                    <a href="/board/request" class="btn btn-primary w-100 mt-3">바로가기</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card h-100 board-card">
                <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
                    <h3 class="card-title h5 fw-bold">구인 게시판</h3>
                    <p class="card-text text-muted small">같이 게임 할 사람 찾기</p>
                    <a href="/board/gather" class="btn btn-primary w-100 mt-3">바로가기</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card h-100 board-card border-primary">
                <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
                    <h3 class="card-title h5 fw-bold text-primary">전체 글 보기</h3>
                    <p class="card-text text-muted small">모든 게시판의 글을 한눈에 모아볼 수 있습니다.</p>
                    <a href="/board" class="btn btn-outline-primary w-100 mt-3">모아보기</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>

<footer class="text-center py-4 text-muted border-top bg-white">
    <div class="container">
        <p class="mb-0 small">&copy; 2026 My Service. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</footer>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>